Busstop panel focus :
	- after the panel in search panel is clicked, this one is opened below
	- the panel must have :
		- bus stop number
		- JScrollBar of next buses with their arrival time
		- every bus has the number of seats displayed
		- the buses are clickable (hopefully) and they will open a bus panel on top of the busstop one

Bus panel focus :
	- (NOT SURE) after the bus is clicked this one is opened on the same place as the busstop one
	- the panel must have :
